OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcould change second hand   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbuying habits              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Love Island's decision to dress        
OL,6, contestants in second hand clothes from
OL,7, eBay could spark a change in viewers'  
OL,8, shopping habits, fashion experts say.  
OL,10,FThe show had attracted criticism from  
OL,11,Fsustainability advocates for promoting 
OL,12,Ffast fashion with previous sponsors    
OL,13,Flike Missguided and I Saw It First.    
OL,15,FBut a new partnership with eBay UK     
OL,16,Fcould change the way its viewers shop, 
OL,17,Fsaid fashion consultant Natalie Binns. 
OL,19,FThe show's bosses said it was striving 
OL,20,Fto be "a more eco-friendly production."
